        <p>Tumor in left knee, pinkish in color, measuring 3 cm in major axis</p>
      </caption>
      <graphic xlink:href="abd-90-06-0907-g01"/>
    </fig>
    <fig id="f2" orientation="portrait" position="float">
      <label>Figure 2</label>
      <caption>
        <p>Histologic examination (x100): epidermis with moderate irregular acanthosis,
dermis with lymphohistiocytic infiltrate presenting granulomatous outline
and some giant cells containing muriform bodies (detail, x 400)</p>
      </caption>
      <graphic xlink:href="abd-90-06-0907-g02"/>
    </fig>
    <fig id="f3" orientation="portrait" position="float">
      <label>Figure 3</label>
